20drones%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2060%2C000%20passengers%20had%20their%20flights%20delayed%20or%20canceled%20at%20airports%20across%20Russia%20as%20Ukraine%20unleashed%20large-scale%20drone%20attacks%20this%20week%2C%20according%20to%20a%20national%20tourism%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20association%20of%20tour%20operators%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.atorus.ru%2Farticle%2Fotmeny-i-zaderzhki-reysov-povliyali-na-plany-ne-menee-60-tysyach-passazhirov-62026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20at%20least%20350%20flights%20were%20affected%20by%20the%20threat%20of%20drone%20strikes%2C%20including%20trips%20out%20of%20the%20country%20to%20destinations%20such%20as%20Istanbul%20and%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20affected%20facilities%20included%20Moscow's%20four%20airports%20and%20air%20travel%20hubs%20in%20the%20regions%20of%20Sochi%2C%20Kazan%2C%20and%20Kirov%2C%20per%20the%20association.%20Its%20statement%20said%20many%20of%20the%20flights%20were%20delayed%20overnight%2C%20while%20some%20flights%20that%20did%20manage%20to%20depart%20had%20to%20wait%20up%20to%20seven%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20independent%20Telegram%20news%20channels%20posted%20photos%20of%20large%20crowds%20gathering%20in%20airports%20and%20stranded%20passengers%20resting%20in%20departure%20hall%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20delay%20will%20provoke%20subsequent%20delays%20according%20to%20the%20domino%20principle%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20tourism%20operators'%20association%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20aviation%20infrastructure%20is%20working%20at%20its%20limit%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20advised%20travelers%20across%20the%20country%20to%20prepare%20for%20further%20disruption%20by%20bringing%20cash%20to%20buy%20food%20and%20drink%20at%20airports%20and%20taking%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20supply%26quot%3B%20of%20water%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chaos%20comes%20as%20Russia%20is%20set%20to%20hold%20an%20annual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussias-red-square-military-parade-again-had-only-one-tank-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVictory%20Day%20parade%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20May%209%20that%20commemorates%20the%20Soviet%20Union's%20role%20in%20ending%20World%20War%20II%20%E2%80%94%20a%20major%20source%20of%20national%20pride%20promoted%20by%20Moscow%20nowadays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20says%20it's%20expecting%2029%20world%20leaders%20to%20attend%20the%20parade%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-xi-jinping-meeting-private-sector-big-tech-personal-approval-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese%20leader%20Xi%20Jinping%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20arrived%20on%20Wednesday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Kyiv%20has%20warned%20visiting%20leaders%20that%20it%20can't%20guarantee%20their%20safety%20if%20they%20fly%20into%20Moscow%2C%20which%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoscow-drone-attack-wakes-up-russians-fear-of-war-expert-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eharassed%20by%20Ukrainian%20drone%20strikes%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20be%20held%20responsible%20for%20what%20happens%20on%20the%20territory%20of%20the%20Russian%20Federation%2C%26quot%3B%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20told%20reports%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20week%20leading%20up%20to%20Russia's%20Victory%20Day%20parade%20has%20seen%20Ukraine%20launch%20an%20intensified%20series%20of%20drone%20strikes%20over%20three%20consecutive%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20appear%20to%20be%20ramping%20up%20in%20severity%2C%20with%20the%20Kremlin%20saying%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20it%20shot%20down%20524%20drones.%20Business%20Insider%20couldn't%20independently%20verify%20that%20figure%2C%20but%20if%20accurate%2C%20it%20would%20record%20one%20of%20Ukr