n%20my%20face%20and%20neglecting%20my%20body.%20These%20days%2C%20I've%20been%20slathering%20on%20this%20body%20balm%20and%20loving%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20body%20lotions%2C%20which%20can%20feel%20a%20bit%20heavy%20and%20leave%20an%20unpleasant%20film%20on%20my%20skin%2C%20this%20product%20feels%20more%20serum-like.%20It%20has%20a%20very%20subtle%20floral%20scent%20that%20I%20love%20and%20glides%20on%20so%20smoothly%20without%20a%20sticky%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20rubbing%20this%20every%20morning%20on%20my%20belly%20during%20pregnancy%20to%20try%20and%20ward%20off%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fpregnancy-stretch-marks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estretch%20marks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20on%20my%20thighs%20where%20I%20tend%20to%20notice%20more%20crepiness%20and%20saggy%20skin.%20But%20when%20I%20have%20time%2C%20I%20apply%20it%20all%20over%20my%20body.%20It%20feels%20like%20the%20ultimate%20act%20of%20self-care%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20super%20impressed%20that%20my%20skin%20still%20feels%20supremely%20soft%2C%20supple%2C%20and%20hydrated%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20eight%20to%2010%20hours%20after%20I%20applied%20the%20balm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20formula%20contains%20a%20powerhouse%20blend%20of%20moisturizers%3A%20jojoba%20oil%2C%20olive%20oil%2C%20and%20vitamin%20E-rich%20oil.%20It%20also%20features%20argan%20oil%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC5019162%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20shown%20to%20improve%20skin%20elasticity%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20thereby%20prevent%20and%20reduce%20stretch%20marks.%20Another%20ingredient%20worth%20mentioning%20is%20glycogen%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC8367632%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupports%20the%20production%20of%20ceramides%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20moisturizing%20fatty%20acids%20that%20help%20strengthen%20the%20skin%20barrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223248a326-1d5b-47b9-b1f0-c4277b4a8bcd%5C%22%3Eholi%20(bright)%20resurface%20glass%20face%20mask%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20holds%20the%20Agent%20Nateur%20holi%20(bright)%20resurface%20glass%20face%20mask.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681b8e9ca466d2b74ab54a0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Strong%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20hardly%20a%20more%20satisfying%20skincare%20product%20than%20an%20exfoliating%20mask%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20many%20of%20them%20are%20a%20little%20too%20harsh%20on%20my%20sensitive%20skin.%20Holi%20(bright)%20is%20ideal%20for%20dry%20and%20sensitive%20skin%20types%20like%20mine%20because%20it's%20made%20with%20lactic%20acid%20(as%20opposed%20to%20harsher%20AHAs%20like%20glycolic%20acid)%2C%20soothing%20pure%20aloe%20vera%20gel%20and%20cucumber%2C%20and%20hydrating%20hyaluronic%20acid.%20Other%20noteworthy%20ingredients%20include%20brightening%20vitamin%20C%20and%20moisturizing%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F22189681%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanti-inflammatory%3C%2Fa%3E%20French%20silk%20peptides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoli%20(bright)%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20applied%20to%20clean%20skin%20using%20a%20soft%20mask%20brush%2C%20but%20since%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20brush%2C%20I%20just%20used%20my%20fingers%20to%20create%20a%20thick%2C%20even%20layer%20across%20my%20face%20and%20neck.%20Agent%20Nateur%20recommends%20leaving%20the%20mask%20on%20for%20at%20least%2015-30%20minutes%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20left%20on%20overnight%20for%20more%20dramatic%20results.%20I%20set%20a%20timer%20for%2030%20minutes%20and%20then%20rinsed%20it%20off%20with%20lukewarm%20water.%20The%20scent%20was%20slightly%20medicinal%20%E2%80%94%20not%20my%20favorite%2C%20but%20also%20not%20off-putting%20at%20all.%20I%20noticed%20a%20very%20subtle%20tingling%20sensation%20after%20applying%20it%2C%20but%20before%20I%20could%20get%20nervous%20about%20a%20potential%20reaction%2C%20the%20sensation%20quickly%20went%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%20mask%20dried%20down%20within%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20minutes%2C%20my%20skin%20felt%20incredibly%20tight%2C%20almost%20frozen%20in%20place.%20(I%20wondered%3A%20Is%20this%20what%20Botox%20feels%20like%3F)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20rinsed%20it%20off%2C%20my%20skin%20felt%20flexible%20again%20%E2%80%94%20but%20still%20somehow%20more%20taut%20and%20definitely%20smoother.%20I%20also%20noticed%20the%20pores%20I%20typically%20see%20in%20between%20my%20eyebrows%20and%20on%20my%20cheeks%20weren't%20as%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a7770c2-16ca-4f6e-9805-e557b14ea65f%5C%22%3Eholi%20(oil)%20refining%20ageless%20face%20serum%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20the%20Agent%20Nateur%20holi%20(oil)%20refining%20ageless%20face%20serum%20and%20the%20author%20after%20using%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681b8f593fe8d39283653178%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Strong%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20historically%2C%20I've%20never%20considered%20a%20facial%20oil%20a%20must%20in%20my%20skincare%20routine%2C%20my%20attitude%20has%20been%20steadily%20changing.%20Oils%20seem%20to%20combat%20my%20lifelong%20dryness%20in%20a%20way%20that%20traditional%20moisturizers%20just%20can't.%20Holi%20(oil)%20is%20an%20oil-serum%20hybrid%20that's%20meant%20to%20be%20massaged%20into%20the%20skin%20after%20cleansing%20and%20toning.%20And%20a%20little%20goes%20a%20long%20way%3A%20I%20only%20needed%20about%20four%20to%20five%20drops%20for%20my%20entire%20face%20and%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20oil%20is%20packed%20with%20skin-loving%20ingredients%2C%20like%20rosehip%20and%20oil%2C%20Japanese%20rice%20bran%20oil%2C%20and%20redness-fighting%20as%20well%20as%20moisturizing%20rosa%20damascena%20oil.%20The%20formula%20also%20features%20sodium%20ascorbyl%20phosphate%2C%20a%20gentle%20yet%20potent%20form%20of%20vitamin%20C%20that%20brightens%20the%20skin%20and%20helps%20to%20fade%20hyperpigmentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoli%20(oil)%20smells%20like%20a%20bouquet%20of%20roses%20and%20doesn't%20leave%20me%20with%20that%20dreaded%20greasy%20finish%20I%20get%20with%20so%20many%20other%20facial%20oils.%20It's%20ideal%20on%20days%20when%20my%20skin%20feels%20especially%20dehydrated%2C%20and%20I%20know%20it%20will%20definitely%20come%20in%20handy%20during%20the%20winter.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20remarkable%20things%20I%20noticed%20after%20using%20this%20product%20is%20that%20it%20actually%20calmed%20the%20redness%20around%20my%20nose%20and%20cheeks.%20Plus%2C%20if%20I%20apply%20a%20few%20extra%20drops%2C%20this%20gives%20my%20skin%20just%20enough%20slip%20to%20use%20a%20face-sculpting%20and%20depuffing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fgua-sha%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egua%20sha%3C%2Fa%3E%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fcc7cea9-9462-4767-a8ec-5fcc57ffc80d%5C%22%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20beauty%20brands%20go%2C%20Agent%20Nateur%20is%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bcleanest%26quot%3B%20you'll%20find%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20good%20news%20is%2C%20extensive%20testing%20has%20shown%20me%20that%20the%20brand%20definitely%20doesn't%20sacrifice%20efficacy%20for%20safety.%20The%20quality%20of%20the%20ingredients%20is%20undeniable%2C%20and%20every%20single%20product%20in%20the%20line%20strikes%20a%20perfect%20balance%3A%20gentle%20enough%20for%20sensitive%20skin%2C%20yet%20powerful%20enough%20to%20yield%20real%2C%20noticeable%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20really%20impressed%20with%20my%20results%20from%20the%20Agent%20Nateur%20line%20%E2%80%94%20the%20acid%20(wash)%20cleanser%2C%20holi%20(sun)%20drops%2C%20holi%20(lift)%2C%20and%20body%20balm%20are%20now%20go-tos%20in%20my%20daily%20routine.%20I%20also%20plan%20to%20continue%20incorporating%20holi%20(bright)%20and%20holi%20(oil)%20as%20needed%2C%20and%20I%20expect%20the%20perks%20to%20only%20amplify%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20I'll%20do%20if%20Agent%20Nateur%20discontinues%20the%20holi%20(stick)%20deodorant%20%E2%80%94%20though%20something%20tells%20me%2C%20given%20that%20it's%20the%20brand's%20first%20launch%20and%20a%20consistent%20bestseller%2C%20I%20thankfully%20don't%20see%20that%20happening%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fagent-nateur-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746652736000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681b91f5c6ad288d148047bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fagent-nateur-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I've%20been%20a%20beauty%20writer%20for%209%20years%20and%20I'm%20also%20currently%20pregnant%2C%20so%20I%20came%20in%20with%20a%20very%20critical%20eye%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20turns%20out%20this%20is%20some%20of%20the%20best%20skincare%20I've%20tried.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Strong)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fagent-nateur-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AMC%20Theatres%20Quarterly%20Losses%20Hit%20%24202.1%20Million%20After%20Box%20Office%20Got%20Off%20to%20Rocky%20Start%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746652438000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com