her%20seat%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223227975a-f035-4245-b9eb-1b8c682b2bf1%5C%22%3EHarry%20Potter%20and%20the%20purloined%20merch%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20prospective%20juror%20is%20asked%20whether%20they%20or%20any%20significant%20person%20in%20their%20life%20has%20had%20any%20contact%20with%20law%20enforcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20this%20question%20prompted%20a%20former%20parochial%20school%20teacher%20from%20the%20Bronx%20to%20admit%20to%20her%20juvenile%20shoplifting%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUm%2C%20I%20was%20at%20Universal%20Studios%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20began.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20I%20was%20in%20Harry%20Potter%20World.%20So%2C%20they%20took%20me%20to%20the%20back%20and%2C%20um%2C%20they%20kind%20of%2C%20like%2C%20put%20me%20through%20all%20the%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%2016%2C%20and%20a%20lawyer%20eventually%20got%20the%20case%20reduced%20to%20%26quot%3Bjust%20a%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20judge%20with%20an%20embarrassed-sounding%20laugh.%20Many%20of%20the%20defense%20lawyers%20and%20prosecutors%20couldn't%20resist%20smiling.%20Combs%2C%20too%2C%20smiled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20judge%20broached%20the%20question%20on%20everyone's%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOK%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%2C%20as%20if%20eliciting%20a%20formal%20confession.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20did%20you%20take%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20wand%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20woman%20remained%20a%20contender%20for%20the%20jury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223c338cb3-e10d-4322-9e23-276fcee92233%5C%22%3EJuror%20No.%20420%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20order%20you%20not%20to%20use%20marijuana%20during%20this%20trial%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20told%20a%20prospective%20juror%20who%20works%20as%20a%20landlord%20in%20the%20Bronx%20%E2%80%94%20and%20who%20said%20he%20partakes%20nightly.%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to